<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad VI., Herr von Bickenbach und Burggraf von Miltenberg</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Unterstützung und kündigt Hans Maurer, Diener der Stadt, wegen Gütern Nürnberger Kaufleute an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_282" id="140v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_282_r1l11"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> von Pıckembach etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_282_r1l12">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Als </del> vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wol geſagt vvie ſıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l13"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edel von der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> habe <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒemal <expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweıſet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l14">vnd <expan>ernſtlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darümb <expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab / des wir ew mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l15"><expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / dancken / vnd ſchıcken darümb cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l16">Hanſen <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener mit ew dauon cʒureden / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l17"><expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edel <expan>fleiſſıkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> / vvaʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıener darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l18">cʒu diſem mal an euch werb von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_282" id="140v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> von Pickembach etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wol gesagt, wie sich
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edel von der
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> habe <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czemal
                                <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweiset und
                                <expan>ernstlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darümb
                            <expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab, des wir ew mit
                                <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz dancken, und schicken darümb
                        czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell Hansen
                            <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener,
                        mit ew davon czu reden, und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edel <expan>fleissikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>, waz
                        der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener darümb czu disem mal an euch werb von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
